Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:24.23,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll be there for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:26.98,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}展开双翅翱翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:33.40,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}到那崭新的世界Go with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:41.94,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你我携手迈步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:44.71,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}即便黑夜也可无畏前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:49.46,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}一起去往那无人知晓的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:53.21,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}虽然途中会遭遇暴风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:56.05,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}但你凝视双目所散发出的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:02:00.14,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}给了我向前的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:06.14,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}比魔法还要强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:12.15,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我觉得那是无人所能取代的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:17.44,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这份Power of Love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:20.78,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}因此 I'll be there for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:23.42,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我相信着这份羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:28.96,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你的空虚 你的唇 你那倔强的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:32.05,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我喜欢 Always I Love you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.67,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你我一定可以
