Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:24.23,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll be there for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:26.98,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}羽ばたいてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:33.40,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}新しい世界へGo with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:41.94,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}手と手をつないで進めば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:44.71,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}闇さえ怖れず行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:49.46,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}誰もまだ知らないあの場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:53.21,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}途中で嵐に遭っても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:56.05,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}見守る瞳の明かりが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:02:00.14,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}立ち向かう勇気をくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:06.14,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}魔法より強いチカラさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:12.15,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}かけがえのないキミを想う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:17.44,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}このPower of Love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:20.78,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}だからI'll be there for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:23.42,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}絆を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:28.96,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}寂しさも クチビルも 強気なまなざしも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:32.05,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}好きさ Always I Love you
